      <title>印度煤炭资源丰富的邦将根据法院裁决通过采矿税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/coal-rich-indian-state-to-pass-mining-tax-after-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度贾坎德邦通过了一项征收矿业税的法案，此举将推高煤炭和铝土矿等矿产的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/coal-rich-indian-state-to-pass-mining-tax-after-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国电动汽车调查的推进，欧盟计划对特斯拉汽车征收 9% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/eu-plans-9-tariff-on-tesla-cars-as-china-ev-probe-advances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周二表示，计划对从中国进口的特斯拉汽车征收 9% 的关税，同时欧盟已向汽车制造商通报了其将对从中国进口的电动汽车征收最终关税的决定草案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/eu-plans-9-tariff-on-tesla-cars-as-china-ev-probe-advances</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国强劲的工资增长加剧了欧洲央行的通胀困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/germany-s-strong-wage-growth-adds-to-ecb-s-inflation-struggle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行表示，德国强劲的工资增长势头并未减弱，并可能使通胀维持高位——这对正在努力将价格涨幅恢复至 2% 目标的欧洲央行来说是一个令人担忧的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/germany-s-strong-wage-growth-adds-to-ecb-s-inflation-struggle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储面临美国就业岗位减少多达一百万的局面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/fed-confronts-up-to-a-million-us-jobs-vanishing-in-revision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[截至 3 月份的一年里，美国就业增长可能远低于最初的预期，这可能会加剧人们对美联储降低利率的步伐进一步落后的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/fed-confronts-up-to-a-million-us-jobs-vanishing-in-revision</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
